# isSensitive

**Instance Property**

A Boolean value that indicates if checked content contains nudity.

## Declaration

```swift
var isSensitive: Bool { get }
```

## Discussion

The framework indicates that content is sensitive only when the active [doc://com.apple.SensitiveContentAnalysis/documentation/SensitiveContentAnalysis/SCSensitivityAnalyzer/analysisPolicy] is a value other than [doc://com.apple.SensitiveContentAnalysis/documentation/SensitiveContentAnalysis/SCSensitivityAnalysisPolicy/disabled].
